### Data Model (MongoDB)
```js
Notification {
  _id: ObjectId,
  entityId: String,     // PostID, UserID, etc.
  userId: String,       // recipient
  type: String,         // "like", "comment", "follow"
  message: String,      // display text
  isRead: Boolean,      // read/unread
  createdAt: Date
}
API Endpoints
POST /notifications â†’ Create a new notification

GET /notifications/:userId â†’ Fetch notifications for a user

PATCH /notifications/:id/read â†’ Mark notification as read

